dc_description_s: This data layer represents land use for Clark County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase 'Clark_LandUse_2014.gdb'. [The data was created through windshield verification. Areas not visible via the road network were checked using aerial photography. All land use classifications include associated features such as accessory buildings, parking facilities, driveways, yards, landscaping, etc. Defined parcels approximately 5.5 acres or less have been designated one land use classification.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
